Package: StanFlowR
Title: Orchestrate Stan Model Workflows via Native CmdStan Command Line
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Carlos", "Traynor", , "carlos.traynor.qcp@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides an end-to-end workflow for Bayesian modeling with Stan
    and Torsten. Prepares model folder structures and data files, compiles Stan
    programs via CmdStan's make system, executes compiled model binaries locally
    or in parallel via MPI, reads CmdStan CSV output files, and extracts
    posterior samples, diagnostics, and predictions for downstream analysis.
    Interfaces directly with CmdStan command-line tools without requiring
    'cmdstanr' or 'rstan' as intermediaries.
License: GPL (>= 3)
URL: https://github.com/csetraynor/StanFlowR
BugReports: https://github.com/csetraynor/StanFlowR/issues
